    <h2 align="left"><font size="4"><img src="images/blank.gif" width="28" height="20"></font><font size="3"><strong>Reflecting on our 50th <br>
    </strong></font><font size="4"><img src="images/blank.gif" width="28" height="20"></font><font size="3"><strong>Anniversary</strong></font></h2>
    </td>
    <td valign="top" width="180"><p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0"><br>
          <br>
          <img src="images/dot.gif" WIDTH="10" HEIGHT="10"><font size="1" face="Arial"><strong><a href="musings_pedalharp.htm">Pedal 
          Harpsichord</a><br>
